    "tour": {
      "id": "380054a3-cb1e-457c-8435-8ee3fd05d2b5",
      "name": "Burj Khalifa Tour Dubai",
      "isFeatured": true,
      "isActive": true,
      "cover_image": "burj_khalifa_2jpg-cd273642-8b68-4160-a06a-c8728faca775",
      "images": [
        "burj_khalifa_alljpg-f1df8f80-2889-489e-93a4-7adcd0520740",
        "burj_khalifajpg-98e05de3-8ee6-43bd-ac56-801eee7072de"
      ],
      "overview": "Witness the views over Dubai from the observation deck of the iconic Burj Khalifa, the world's tallest building. Ascend to the 124th and 125th floors for a panoramic 360-degree view over the Arabian Gulf.",
      "highlights": "Zip up the fastest elevators on the planet to reach the 124th floor of the Burj Khalifa for stunning views of the Dubai skyline.\nLevel up your Dubai trip (literally!) with a visit to the 124 and 125 floors of the Burj Khalifa.\nThe observation deck with floor-to-ceiling windows on the 124th floor gives you 360° views of the Arabian Gulf.\nThe 125th floor ups the ante with an open-air terrace. And don't miss the exquisite Mashrabiya motifs – a tribute to Arab arts and culture.\nFor a luxurious and personalized experience with shorter wait times, upgrade to Sky Lounge access on the 148th floor. You can also include a visit to the Dubai Aquarium & Underwater Zoo.\nFun Fact: The Burj Khalifa features the world's fastest elevator that travels at 10 meters per second, reaching the top in less than a minute.",
